item.description: I run Free Comedy Shows at the Grog in Newburyport Mondays 730 downstairs in the Cabaret! With a line up of the area's best comics,,, from those who have been doing it for a couple years to pro headliners,,, it changes every week,,,and it is a wonderful chance to see some great acts for free.... and a chance for a newcomer to try their stuff on stage! come have dinner & a drink or two downstairs and laught the night away!
